---
title: Sheet Pan Beef & Feta Meatloaves with Tomato Salad, Hummus Sauce & Potato Wedges
description: Don’t let the name fool you: These meatloaves are anything but the boring ones you grew up with (sorry not sorry all grandparents!). We infused tonight’s staple ground beef with a spicy, savory Turkish spice blend, then covered the baked loaves with a garlicky, creamy hummus sauce that’s simply irresistible. Add to that, sides of crisp roasted tater wedges and a classic cuke, tomato, and feta salad—Opa!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sheet-pan-greek-beef-feta-meatloaves-865ca03f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sheet-pan-beef-feta-meatloaves-63459acb1093adecf10f227d-ee13ee00.pdf
